name: Spine AI
long_description:
Enable your internal teams and customers to get insights without burdening your technical teams.

Spine AI effectively translates your business context and data schema into an AI analyst that gives reliable responses to natural language questions.

The AI analyst is equipped with custom-tuned models and a semantic layer to ensure consistently accurate responses. The analysts also show their work, providing transparency and instilling confidence to act on their insights.
one_liner: Reliable AI data analysts that know your business
